# shadcn UI Component Usage

This project uses **shadcn UI** for all UI elements.

## Installation

### Initialize shadcn (if not already initialized)

If shadcn is not initialized in the project, run:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

### Adding Components

When a specific component is not installed, use the following command format:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add <component-name>
```

**Example:** To install the button component:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
```

## Guidelines

- Always use shadcn UI components for UI elements
- Check if a component is already installed before adding it
- shadcn components are typically located in the `components/ui/` directory
- All shadcn components are built on top of Radix UI primitives and styled with Tailwind CSS
